# 🔹 2. Rules for Naming Variables

```python
# VALID VARIABLES

age = 21
_colour = "Lilac"
total_score = 90
myVar = 100
```

```python
# INVALID VARIABLES

# 1name = "Error"     # starts with digit
# class = 10          # keyword
# user-name = "Alex"  # hyphen not allowed
```

---

## 📌 Variable Naming Rules

```python
"""
1. Can contain letters, digits, underscore (_)
2. Cannot start with digit
3. Case-sensitive
4. Cannot use keywords
"""
```

